{"tid":1013722,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[自虐]有無人對自己好差:好姑寒好小家","createTime":"2019-02-08T14:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T06:45:27.000Z","uid":11030,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0630d5beaa1c505e7fec1a963ccc1568112531","tid":1013722,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"買野一定會簡最低價嘅買 意圖用錢過最低限度嘅生活水平 衫唔會買 化妝品用一兩年 電話4年先換一次（不過堅持要用iphone）<br />\n<br />\n食飯唔會食over$50 ，成日比朋友話食狗糧<br />\n為左唔用錢寧願唔約人出街 唔會出市區因爲車費貴<br />\n<br />\n對人都會小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會特別請人食飯 除非對方生日 食飯要暗中計錢<br />\n不過人地要請我我就一定會請番佢 唔會貪人地便宜<br />\n<br />\n儲番嚟嘅錢其實無意義 唔係為買野 係為安心感<br />\n個一日無用到錢就會覺得開心<br />\n肚餓無食到飯個種空虛都會覺得開心<br />\n越傷害左自己就越覺得有成功嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請問我係咪痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話比我知我不是一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57140fc1b6dfd12b25dc8a917ef60423bb3305e3","tid":1013722,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8718e5313135b73c7b31a986fade7b5da7eafb","tid":1013722,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2773f5945edcb1fc66b759bd470ceffbb159fbd5","tid":1013722,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b5c4d63032c526b5583fd3405e7394dd23f921","tid":1013722,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"明明地鐵快啲但寧願搭平少少嘅巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然巴士都坐得舒服d"},{"pid":"bdaa4edb66f6502fdb2c2fd8e1eabeb7c86ca3fa","tid":1013722,"uid":79373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"食50定50000個餐最後都變屎<br />\n覺得食嘢應該只求填肚就得"}]}